#: ../../source/unit/gps_v11.rst:3 b55d8c177e284a4c9f51d29ad1c4d0e0
msgid "GPS V1.1(SMA) Unit"
msgstr "GPS V1.1(SMA) Unit"

#: ../../source/unit/gps_v11.rst:7 62dfd51262f34b379a57bb36fbb01d1d
msgid ""
"GPS Unit v1.1 is a GNSS global positioning navigation unit, integrating "
"the high-performance CASIC navigation chip AT6668 and signal amplifier "
"chip MAX2659, with a built-in ceramic antenna, providing more precise and"
" reliable satellite positioning services."
msgstr ""
"GPS Unit v1.1 是一款 GNSS 全球定位导航单元，集成高性能 CASIC 导航芯片 AT6668 和信号放大器芯片 "
"MAX2659，内置陶瓷天线，可提供更精确、更可靠的卫星定位服务。"

#: ../../source/unit/gps_v11.rst:9 7ff220bd7d564498ae16ff063a978e47
msgid ""
"GPS SMA Unit is a GNSS global positioning navigation unit that integrates"
" the high-performance CASIC navigation chip AT6668 and the signal "
"amplifier chip MAX2659. It uses an external antenna to provide more "
"accurate and reliable satellite positioning services."
msgstr ""
"GPS SMA Unit 是一款 GNSS 全球定位导航单元，集成了高性能 CASIC 导航芯片 AT6668 和信号放大器芯片 "
"MAX2659。它使用外置天线，可提供更准确、更可靠的卫星定位服务。"

